  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, edition source: </div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ἐνθάδε κῖτε <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρεῖ\n                    να\">Βικ[τωρεῖ-]<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>να</span> ζήσασα ἒτη <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">λ</span>´ [τελευ-]<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>τᾷ τῇ πρὸ <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ς</span>´ εἰδ(ῶν) [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>Α 𐆠 Ω </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, edition source: </div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΕΝΘΑΔΕΚΙΤΕ<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρεῖ\n                    να\">ΒΙΚ[.....]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΝΑ</span>ΖΗΣΑΣΑΕΤΗ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Λ</span>[.....]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΤΑΤΗΠΡΟ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Σ</span>ΕΙΔ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>Α𐆠Ω</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001349_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001349_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001349.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001349-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text: IG</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>Here lies Biktoreina, having lived for 30 years [...] who died 6 [days] before the Ides [of ...]</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] no.40 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a></li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9492 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">530a</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
